Corporate Values
Customers
Satisfied customers are the key to our success. We pursue total customer satisfaction by understanding our customer’s business, organization, and strategy in an effort to efficiently predict and meet all their requirements.  We will rank among the industry’s most valued suppliers by the customers we serve.
Teamwork
We value the skills, strengths, and perspectives of our diverse global team. We advocate a participatory workplace enabling our associates to make decisions that advance our common business objectives.
Innovation
We strive to be innovative in all that we do.  Innovation and creativity are requirements to deliver value in terms of products and services.  Innovation is a culture throughout the organization which we practice everyday.
Responsibility
We provide a safe workplace and promote the health and well-being of the Lawter family. We encourage associates to volunteer in their communities supporting the causes that they value.  Our business activities will not jeopardize our environment.
Profit
In order to guarantee our future the business must produce a profit generating fair returns on the assets entrusted to us by our shareholders.
Integrity
We always choose the high road by practicing the highest ethical standards and by honoring our commitments. We take personal responsibility for our actions, and treat everyone fairly with trust, dignity and respect.
Philosophy
















